  "texts": [
    "We hope this deeper analysis will inform researchers and practitioners aiming to improve financial LM performance.",
    "In addition to the aggregate results, we highlight some error patterns: Outdated or Degenerate Behavior (Llama 2 13B Chat).",
    "During certain classification tasks, LLAMA 2 13B occasionally produces near-empty or trivial outputs (e.g., \"Sure.",
    "\"), offering zero signal.",
    "Such degenerate behavior suggests possible corruption or misalignment in the fine-tuning stage."
  ]
}